Thyphon/Elektra::

Underwater two bots were watting around Iron Fist.

Thyphon aand Elektra was a round the Iron First Scanners, but they 
weren't detected because they were several feet far of scanners' area.
Thyphon saw a body in water surface and he was ready to fight...

His beast mode was a sea dragon, his body was like snake and the head 
like a dragon. his body's color was black with bright red eyes. His 
fangs were sharped and his main fangs (four front fans)were bigger 
than others, inside them he had his cyber vemon that was able to kill 
in few minutes a bot with 16 feet.


A femme was near of THyphon, whose name was Elektra.


"Be ready Elektra..." said the male "We can be involve in a battle 
soon..."
